Package eu.geclipse.ui.dialogs

Class Summary
AuthTokenInfoDialog A dialog that presents information about authentication tokens to the user.
ConfigureFiltersDialog Dialog, which allow user to make filter configurations
GridFileDialog This is an implementation of a file dialog for browsing remote connections via EFS that are defined in the ConnectionManager.
Messages Returns the localised messages for this package.
NewCaCertDialog Dialog that is used by the CA certificate preference page in order to import CA certificates.
NewProblemDialog The ProblemDialog is the graphical front-end for the g-Eclipse problem reporting mechanism.
PasswordDialog A simple password dialog for soliciting a password string from the user.
